Package uk.msci.project.rsa

Class StatisticData

java.lang.Object
uk.msci.project.rsa.StatisticData
public class StatisticData extends Object
The StatisticData class represents a single statistic, including its name and value, for display in the results view. This class supports both single-value and multi-value statistics.
